:: iMod Widget OrphanageCanteen [widget]
<<widget "OrphanageCanteenEntrance">>
	<<set _link to lanSwitch("Orphanage Canteen", "孤儿院食堂") + '(00:01)'>>
	<<link _link "Orphanage Canteen">>
		<<pass 1>>
	<</link>>
<</widget>>

:: Orphanage Canteen [scene]

<div id='locationdes'>
<<if (!$tvar.scene.passage || $tvar.scene.type == 'Scene') and $phase is 0>>
	<<set _output to "Orphanage Canteen localDescription " + setup.language>>
	<<include _output>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>
</div>

<div id='content'>
	<<if $tvar.scene.passage>>
		<<include $tvar.scene.passage>>
	<<elseif Time.hour >= 18 && Time.hour <= 19>> 
		<<include 'Scene Orphanage Canteen'>>
	<</if>>
</div>

<br><br><br>

<<set _link to lanSwitch("have a dinner", "吃顿饭") + '(00:30)'>>
<<if Time.hour >= 18 && Time.hour <= 19>>
	<<link _link "Orphanage Canteen Eat">>
		<<run V.thirst -=1000;V.hunger -=1000;>>
		<<pass 30>>
	<</link>>
<</if>>
<br>

<<set _link2 = getLan('leave')>>
	<<getouticon>><<link _link2 "Orphanage">>
	<</link>>    
	
:: Orphanage Canteen Eat
<<widget "OrphanageCanteenEat">>
	<<include '你在孤儿院食堂饱餐了一顿'>><<llhunger>><<llthirst>>
<</widget>>

<br><br><br>

<<set _link to lanSwitch("Orphanage Canteen", "孤儿院食堂")>>
	<<link _link "Orphanage Canteen">>
	<</link>>

:: Orphanage Canteen localDescription CN
你来到了孤儿院的食堂。
<<if Time.hour < 18 || Time.hour > 19>>
	这个时间食堂里面空荡荡，一个人都没有。如果要吃饭的话记得18:00-19:00来。
<</if>>

:: Orphanage Canteen localDescription EN
You come to the canteen.
<<if Time.hour < 18 || Time.hour > 19>>
	The canteem is closed at this time, and there is no one inside.If you want to eat, remember to come from 18:00 to 19:00.
<</if>>

